---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Contact — Primorum" reading={true}>
  <p class="eyebrow">Primorum &mdash; Contact</p>
  <h1>One human in the loop.</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    Primorum is run by a single principal. The fastest way through is email. The slowest is
    anything else.
  </p>

  <dl class="contact-grid">
    <dt>Principal</dt>
    <dd>Brendan Ardagh</dd>

    <dt>Email</dt>
    <dd><a href="mailto:brendan@primorum.ai">brendan@primorum.ai</a></dd>

    <dt>Office</dt>
    <dd>
      Zemlar Offices<br />
      1200 Bay Street<br />
      Toronto, Ontario, Canada
    </dd>

    <dt>Domain</dt>
    <dd>primorum.ai</dd>
  </dl>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <p>
    Good signal: a sharp critique of the <a href="/thesis">thesis</a>, a distribution channel we
    have not noticed, an AI-native business shape we should be running as a spike, or an
    operator-grade collaborator who wants to ship.
  </p>

  <p>
    Bad signal: pitch decks, recruitment, partnership outreach with no specific ask. We respond to
    those rarely and slowly.
  </p>
</Base>
